30typedef struct rdp_pointer_cache rdpPointerCache;
31
32#include <freerdp/cache/cache.h>

34struct rdp_pointer_cache
35{
36 uint32 cacheSize; /* 0 */
37 rdpPointer** entries; /* 1 */
38
39 /* internal */
40
41 rdpUpdate* update;
42 rdpSettings* settings;
43};
